have to pay for his keep...

11:09.875 --> 11:11.749
Because he is a loser.

11:11.750 --> 11:14.291
In 20 years he couldn't get tenure.

11:14.292 --> 11:16.416
How anyone besides me,

11:16.417 --> 11:19.699
