11:19.700 --> 11:21.416
It's stupefying.

11:21.417 --> 11:22.874
So you are upset.

11:22.875 --> 11:24.842
No, I'm not.

11:25.583 --> 11:27.550
I'm disgusted.

11:36.333 --> 11:39.008
You're gonna stay for dinner?

11:40.542 --> 11:42.717
- Well, I...
