Would you cheat on her?

01:08:07.000 --> 01:08:09.092
No, I would never.

01:08:10.833 --> 01:08:13.258
Darwan, you're a good man.

01:08:15.000 --> 01:08:16.499
You give me faith.

01:08:16.500 --> 01:08:17.666
Thank you.

01:08:17.667 --> 01:08:19.716
No, I... I don't want this any-more.

01:08:20.832 --> 01:08:23.300
I don't know how to talk to her.

01:08:27.125 --> 01:08:28.791
She's not educated.

01:08:28.792 --> 01:08:30.499
We don't like the same things at all.

01:08:30.500 --> 01:08:31.841
She's...

01:08:33.707 --> 01:08:37.425
She's scared of America.
She's scared of me, she hides.

01:08:40.417 --> 01:08:42.550
You know words, Wendy.

01:08:43.832 --> 01:08:45.675
What do I say?

01:08:49.042 --> 01:08:50.758
That you...

01:08:52.000 --> 01:08:54.383
You never stop trying.

01:08:56.167 --> 01:08:58.383
That you fight for her.

01:09:00.417 --> 01:09:04.300
Everyday you tread across the divide.

01:09:06.292 --> 01:09:08.716
Because she's worth that.

01:09:12.167 --> 01:09:14.508
Is this what you want to hear from him?

01:09:16.750 --> 01:09:18.591
Not words.

01:09:24.500 --> 01:09:26.341
You know what I miss?

01:09:29.832 --> 01:09:32.341
The way he touch my face.

01:09:34.917 --> 01:09:36.591
Just...

01:09:38.250 --> 01:09:41.508
holding my face between his two hands.

01:09:51.750 --> 01:09:53.999
Can you come inside? I left my chequebook.

01:09:54.000 --> 01:09:56.300
You can pay me next time.

01:09:58.917 --> 01:10:00.675
No next time.

01:10:02.000 --> 01:10:04.383
I'm done with driving.

01:10:07.000 --> 01:10:10.883
You shouldn't give up, you only
need a little more practice.

01:10:12.417 --> 01:10:15.383
No, I don't have it in me, Darwan.

01:10:16.458 --> 01:10:18.217
I'm sorry.

01:10:19.708 --> 01:10:22.008
You make me say goodbye.

01:10:22.792 --> 01:10:24.967
I guess. Yeah.

01:10:31.125 --> 01:10:32.550
Thank you.

01:10:32.750 --> 01:10:34.550
You did your best.

01:10:35.500 --> 01:10:37.383
Not enough.

01:10:44.625 --> 01:10:46.300
Goodbye, Wendy.

01:11:47.750 --> 01:11:49.425
What is this...?

01:11:49.458 --> 01:11:51.383
I can't read that!

01:11:53.042 --> 01:11:54.633
Sorry?

01:12:06.292 --> 01:12:08.499
You see the picture, you
know what she wants.

01:12:08.500 --> 01:12:10.217
No, ma'am.

01:12:10.333 --> 01:12:14.383
You work here, and you don't know
where is the sanitary napkin?

01:12:14.625 --> 01:12:16.342
Aisle-five.

01:12:17.333 --> 01:12:19.425
Oh! They are so rude here.

01:12:21.333 --> 01:12:24.300
You have to demand your respect in America.

01:12:25.333 --> 01:12:27.092
Where are you from?

01:12:27.958 --> 01:12:30.717
- Dadiala.
- Ah, my uncle lives there.

01:12:31.000 --> 01:12:33.717
Why don't I see you at the temple, darling?

01:12:42.542 --> 01:12:45.217
How many days have you been married?

01:12:46.750 --> 01:12:48.383
Enough.

01:12:53.958 --> 01:12:55.383
Mata.

01:12:55.667 --> 01:12:57.082
There he is.

01:12:57.083 --> 01:12:58.832
Mata, hello.

01:12:58.833 --> 01:13:02.133
Darwan Singh, why do you shut
up this pearl in the house?

01:13:02.250 --> 01:13:05.582
I assure you she is free to go anywhere.

01:13:05.583 --> 01:13:07.832
What a husband? Leaving
you alone all the time.

01:13:07.833 --> 01:13:10.082
Don't worry, darling.
We'll make our own fun here.

01:13:10.083 --> 01:13:11.842
We don't need him.

01:13:12.250 --> 01:13:15.133
- I'll make dinner.
- Never mind, Jasleen.

01:13:15.583 --> 01:13:18.425
Never mind. Enjoy your new friends.

01:13:18.458 --> 01:13:20.675
I'll pick up something to eat.

01:13:23.000 --> 01:13:24.999
That is right. Leave her to us.

01:13:25.000 --> 01:13:27.700
You won't recognize her
when we're done with her.

01:13:28.000 --> 01:13:31.383
- I'm going.
- Go, go, you're ruining our fun.

01:13:37.000 --> 01:13:38.800
Arghh! So much stuff!

01:13:39.208 --> 01:13:41.249
Believe me! I threw out tons.

01:13:41.250 --> 01:13:44.916
Tasha, thank you for helping, but I
think you have to get back on the road.

01:13:44.917 --> 01:13:47.300
You have a long drive.

01:13:48.292 --> 01:13:50.192
I don't think I'm gonna go back.

01:13:52.917 --> 01:13:55.041
- What?
- I love farming, but I...

01:13:55.042 --> 01:13:58.633
Mainly was there to be
with this guy, and now...

01:13:59.833 --> 01:14:02.624
suddenly, he's decided
to go back to Dartmouth.

01:14:02.625 --> 01:14:06.383
So I'm all alone and all
my friends are gone.

01:14:08.542 --> 01:14:10.925
I'm just so embarrassed.

01:14:13.000 --> 01:14:14.550
Come here.

01:14:15.375 --> 01:14:17.758
Can I stay here with you?

01:14:19.000 --> 01:14:21.050
Oh, I would love that.

01:14:24.042 --> 01:14:26.300
I would so love that.

01:14:26.583 --> 01:14:28.041
But you can't.

01:14:28.042 --> 01:14:30.508
Tasha, if you move in here,

01:14:31.083 --> 01:14:35.383
You would be in a spirit of
failure and that's deadly.

01:14:37.792 --> 01:14:40.124
You have to see this thing through.

01:14:40.125 --> 01:14:44.550
You have to go back to Vermont
and harvest your ass off.

01:14:45.292 --> 01:14:48.467
- I'll come visit you, I promise.
- Okay.

01:14:49.125 --> 01:14:53.092
- It's too far.
- I'm gonna find way, I'm gonna...

01:14:55.167 --> 01:14:56.758
I'm gonna find a way.

01:14:57.458 --> 01:14:59.842
Hi, its Wendy.

01:15:07.292 --> 01:15:09.467
I'm gonna try again.

01:15:11.042 --> 01:15:12.467
Yes.

01:15:19.125 --> 01:15:20.624
How is Jasleen?

01:15:20.625 --> 01:15:22.508
She's very busy.

01:15:22.750 --> 01:15:25.800
She goes to school now, taking classes.

01:15:30.417 --> 01:15:33.133
So, how do you like your new apartment?

01:15:33.583 --> 01:15:36.717
It's an adjustment, I'm tasting it.

01:15:43.500 --> 01:15:47.383
- You're so quiet.
- You're not doing anything wrong.

01:16:13.333 --> 01:16:15.425
Played a chicken meat.

01:16:16.417 --> 01:16:18.592
That looks like a pass.

01:16:22.042 --> 01:16:24.758
- I wish you had been there.
- I was there.

01:16:25.375 --> 01:16:27.416
Thank you, ma'am. I was there.

01:16:27.417 --> 01:16:28.749
Thank you.

01:16:28.750 --> 01:16:30.041
I was there.

01:16:30.042 --> 01:16:32.707
Did you hear my voice
telling you what to do? No.

01:16:32.708 --> 01:16:35.633
- You didn't need it.
- No.

01:16:35.750 --> 01:16:37.332
<i>Oh my God...</i>

01:16:37.333 --> 01:16:38.999
I don't know...

01:16:39.000 --> 01:16:42.457
I just... I wasn't as nervous this time.

01:16:42.458 --> 01:16:44.999
<i>- That's so amazing.</i>
- Yeah.

01:16:45.000 --> 01:16:47.291
<i>- So happy for you, Mum.</i>
- Thanks.

01:16:47.292 --> 01:16:49.124
<i>So, when are you gonna drive up and see me?</i>

01:16:49.125 --> 01:16:50.199
I'm coming soon.

01:16:50.200 --> 01:16:53.082
- It's an classic American car.
- It's a good price.

01:16:53.083 --> 01:16:54.299
Can't go wrong with that.

01:16:54.300 --> 01:16:56.707
You could drive this one
right off the lot today.

01:16:56.708 --> 01:16:58.958
You know, if you're
okay with the colour.

01:16:59.167 --> 01:17:01.249
I never thought about red, but...

01:17:01.250 --> 01:17:02.457
Red is happy, it's...

01:17:02.458 --> 01:17:05.832
what the bride wears for
her wedding in India.

01:17:05.833 --> 01:17:08.425
Yes, but what does it say about me?

01:17:08.833 --> 01:17:10.717
I'm a hot little number?

01:17:11.292 --> 01:17:13.300
Hussie on board?

01:17:13.542 --> 01:17:15.300
It says...

01:17:16.833 --> 01:17:19.217
"Don't fuck with me."

01:17:28.667 --> 01:17:32.207
Allright now, who'd be purchasing the
car today, Sir? You or your wife?

01:17:32.208 --> 01:17:34.675
Ah... She's not my wife.

01:17:36.417 --> 01:17:39.541
But... Whose name will
the car be under, Sir?

01:17:39.542 --> 01:17:40.957
Really, we're not together.

01:17:40.958 --> 01:17:43.008
Honey, it's okay.

01:17:45.500 --> 01:17:48.133
- I'm buying it.
- Allright.

01:17:49.708 --> 01:17:52.092
- Congratulations.
- Oh, thanks.

01:17:54.042 --> 01:17:55.467
How do I...?

01:17:56.250 --> 01:17:57.707
How do I get home?

01:17:57.708 --> 01:18:00.258
You can follow me to the bridge.

01:18:01.083 --> 01:18:02.883
Darwan.

01:18:03.208 --> 01:18:05.633
Darwan, thank you.

01:18:07.167 --> 01:18:10.217
I'll be hearing your voice in my head

01:18:10.458 --> 01:18:11.925
for a long time.

01:18:12.208 --> 01:18:14.425
That would please me.

01:18:15.417 --> 01:18:16.967
Well,

01:18:18.083 --> 01:18:19.675
here I go.

01:18:19.917 --> 01:18:21.383
Wendy.

01:18:24.000 --> 01:18:25.457
Could we go...?

01:18:25.458 --> 01:18:29.457
Somewhere we can celebrate,
a dinner, please?

01:18:29.458 --> 01:18:32.666
Or just a coffee sometime, just to chat.

01:18:32.667 --> 01:18:35.041
- I can't.
- I want to see you again.

01:18:35.042 --> 01:18:36.675
I know.

01:18:40.000 --> 01:18:41.842
The trouble is...

01:18:41.917 --> 01:18:43.550
What?

01:18:43.708 --> 01:18:45.300
What?

01:18:48.542 --> 01:18:50.842
You're a good man.

01:18:55.167 --> 01:18:57.300
You're my faith.

01:19:12.333 --> 01:19:13.967
Wendy.

01:19:14.333 --> 01:19:16.508
Seat belt first.

01:20:26.333 --> 01:20:27.758
Darwan.

01:20:30.792 --> 01:20:32.800
I didn't expect you.

01:21:08.042 --> 01:21:09.675
Jasleen,

01:21:10.250 --> 01:21:13.675
maybe I would not work at night any-more.

01:21:14.417 --> 01:21:16.300
Would you like that?

01:21:28.125 --> 01:21:29.550
Yes.

